title: What music are you listening to?
content:
This is just one of those "What music are you listening to?" posts.

Now: Pink Floyd - Money
Next: Bjrk - Army of MeAustralia, n. A country lying in the South Sea, whose industrial and commercial development has been unspeakably retarded by an unfortunate dispute among geographers as to whether it is a continent or an island.
Thomas Nashe
- The Devil's Dictionary
